#! -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

_FLATFIELD_

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  _FLATFIELD_ 

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive applies the flatfield correction to all files in the
current frame.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

...

=head1 FILE SUFFIX

Creates output files with a '_ff' suffix.

